}, {\"sentence\": \"He was 27.79 seconds behind and will rue his misfortune.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his misfortune\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American riderBrandon McNultywas fifth, with Stefan Bissegger (Switzerland) sixth.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 832, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999977137002803, \"rank\": 2.1463901144602517e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 877, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stefan_Bissegger\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stefan Bissegger\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stefan_Bissegger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stefan_Bissegger\"}, {\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9552069074311883, \"rank\": 0.03765314064919191, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_Switzerland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fifth\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Evenepoel is already the world champion in the discipline, and now adds Olympic success to his list of achievements.\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Evenepoel\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"the world champion\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"the discipline\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic success\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"his list\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"achievements\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I cannot describe the feeling I had on the podium,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the feeling\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a magical moment in my life.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a magical moment\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We watched the women's race before we got into our warm-up and we saw the crashes so we decided not to take any risks in the corners and to push a bit more on the straights, and it was a good strategy.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's race\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"our warm-up\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"the crashes\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"any risks\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"the corners\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"the straights\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"a good strategy\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With a third spot in the Tour de France and a victory here, tiredness does not matter.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1362, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999736490660703, \"rank\": 2.5064354869395086e-05, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a third spot\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"a victory\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"tiredness\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The motivation and the positive feelings overtake everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The motivation\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"the positive feelings\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ganna was just over ten seconds back.\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ganna\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite going so close to a gold medal, he was satisfied with his ride.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"his ride\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is better than the last Games.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last Games\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am really happy,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As everyone knows, I am not super strong with the rain, with not good weather.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"the rain\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1721}, {\"ngram\": \"not good weather\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in the end I tried to follow my dream, I tried to follow the pacing and everything.\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"my dream\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"the pacing\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am really happy for today.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously just a few seconds is a little bit of pain, but in the end we try tonight to celebrate the news of second place.\\\"\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a few seconds\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"the news\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"second place\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for Van Aert, he too was happy.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van Aert\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really dreamed of taking a medal in the time trial,\\\" he said, according to Sporza.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2107, \"end\": 2113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sporza\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sporza\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sporza\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sporza\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"the time trial\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's 'only' bronze, but there are few who can say that.\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very proud of that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He used two disk wheels in the test and said afterward that these made a difference, helping him to beat Tarling.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two disk wheels\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2222}, {\"ngram\": \"the test\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"a difference\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latter's puncture was of course also a factor in the two second gap between them.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latter's puncture\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2334}, {\"ngram\": \"a factor\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"the two second gap\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was confident it was the right choice.\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right choice\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was always comfortable,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"According to the tests, it benefits up to 17 watts.\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tests\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 17 watts\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is considerable, because all the little things like the helmet and the clothes are always one watt extra.\\\"\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the little things\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"the helmet\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2604}, {\"ngram\": \"the clothes\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's Olympic time trial was run off in the same testing conditions as the women but, perhaps informed by the crashes the latter had experienced before them, were less plagued by falls.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The men's Olympic time trial\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"the same testing conditions\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2723}, {\"ngram\": \"the women\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2736}, {\"ngram\": \"the crashes\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2773}, {\"ngram\": \"falls\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The riders still had to exercise caution on the course, avoiding the white lines where possible and taking the safest possible lines through the many corners.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 3001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The riders\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"caution\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2883}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"the white lines\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"the safest possible lines\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2975}, {\"ngram\": \"the many corners\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite that Magnus Sheffied (USA) was unlucky to be involved in a crash.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Magnus Sheffied\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3031}, {\"ngram\": \"USA\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"a crash\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"British favorite Josh Tarling was delayed for another reason, needing a bike change after a puncture.\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3077, \"end\": 3084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9458762980507922, \"rank\": 0.04343450202558653, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3094, \"end\": 3098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9949878140744316, \"rank\": 0.005034886205011941, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another reason\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3137}, {\"ngram\": \"a bike change\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3160}, {\"ngram\": \"a puncture\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This saw him only fourth at the first checkpoint, with several of the big names still to go through that point, leaving him on the back foot and trying to make up time as the TT continued.\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3355, \"end\": 3357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"score\": 0.999999999834472, \"rank\": 1.4514057595228427e-10, \"text\": \"TT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first checkpoint\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3228}, {\"ngram\": \"the big names\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3259}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3290}, {\"ngram\": \"the back foot\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3320}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wout Van Aert (Belgium) was tearing around the course, setting provisional best times at the first and second time checks.\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3385, \"end\": 3392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9991214531116986, \"rank\": 0.000879319079847847, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wout Van Aert\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3423}, {\"ngram\": \"provisional best times\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3455}, {\"ngram\": \"the first and second time checks\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However first Ganna and then Evenepoel went quicker at the first intermediate, threatening his gold medal prospects.\", \"from\": 3493, \"to\": 3609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases